80 TEST_F(EndEffectorTestSuite, getButtonState)
81 {
82  auto ee_state = ee_interface->getEndEffectorState();
83  ASSERT_NE(ee_state, nullptr);
84 
85  auto buttons = ee_state->getButtonsStatus();
86  ASSERT_TRUE(buttons.at(0)->type != common::model::EButtonType::UNKNOWN);
87  ASSERT_TRUE(buttons.at(1)->type != common::model::EButtonType::UNKNOWN);
88  ASSERT_TRUE(buttons.at(2)->type != common::model::EButtonType::UNKNOWN);
89 
90  bool updated_status;
91  for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++)
92  {
93  updated_status = !buttons.at(0)->actions.empty();
94  if (updated_status)
95  break;
96  }
97  ASSERT_TRUE(updated_status);
98 }
